      <comment>/* How do I get the Open File item on the File menu into my platform application? */</comment>
      <text xml:space="preserve">__NOTOC__
===How do I get the Open File item on the File menu into my platform application?===

The Open File menu item is a part of the '''User Utilities''' module, in the &lt;tt&gt;ide&lt;/tt&gt; cluster.
This module can be added to your project using the '''Libraries''' page of the module property sheet. It must be also added to the suite (your suite &gt; Project properties, Libraries &gt; ide &gt; User Utilities)

The '''User Utilities''' module also adds the '''Find in Files''' feature and support for PDF files (they are recognized and can be opened by double-clicking on them).</text>
